title: TrendleBells 12/17: RFK Jr., 51 Senators, Keanu Reeves, Voting Rights, Omicron, Guy Fieri

description:
In this edition of TrendleBells, Jack and Miles discuss RFK Jr. blaming party vaccine request on Cheryl Hines, the 51 senators halting Biden's agenda, Keanu explaining the 'Sad Keanu' meme, voting rights or lack thereof, the NY Omicron surge, and what Guy Fieri eats at home.
